Usage: setDbGetMode [-help] [-reset] [-displayFormat {simple|table}]
                    [-displayLimit <value>] [-escapeBusChar {true|false}]

-help                           # Prints out the command usage
-reset                          # Resets all or specified options to default value
-displayFormat {simple|table}   # How to present the objects and attributes on
                                # stdout  (enums={simple table}, default=simple)
-displayLimit <value>           # Number of objects to be shown with dbGet 
                                # (int, default=10)
-escapeBusChar {true|false}     # Whether to escape bus characters
                                # (bool, default=true)